#

Honey-Glazed Salmon with Asparagus

$18.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodHealthyDinner

Description

Succulent salmon fillets glazed with a sweet and tangy honey sauce, paired with roasted asparagus for a delightful meal.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • Honey: 3 tablespoons
  • Soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
